          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-875-020B-line-1" n="1">We give the World to understand</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-875-020B-line-2" n="2">Our thriveing Dean has purchas'd Land</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-875-020B-line-3" n="3">A purchase which will bring him clear</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-875-020B-line-4" n="4">Above his Rent four pound a Year</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-875-020B-line-5" n="5">Provided to improve the ground</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-875-020B-line-6" n="6">He will but add two Hundred pound</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-875-020B-line-7" n="7">And from his endless hoarded Store</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-875-020B-line-8" n="8">To build a House five Hundred more</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-875-020B-line-9" n="9">Sir Arthur too shall have his Will</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-875-020B-line-10" n="10">And call the Mansion Drapiers Hill</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-875-020B-line-11" n="11">That when a Nation long enslav'd</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-875-020B-line-12" n="12">Forgets by whom it once was sav'd</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-875-020B-line-13" n="13">When none the Drapers praise shall Sing</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-875-020B-line-14" n="14">His Signs aloft no longer Swing</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-875-020B-line-15" n="15">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-875-020B-line-16" n="16">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-875-020B-line-17" n="17">His Medals and his prints forgotten</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-875-020B-line-18" n="18">And all his Handkercheifs are rotten</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-875-020B-line-19" n="19">His famous letters made wast paper</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-875-020B-line-20" n="20">This Hill shall keep the name of Draper</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-875-020B-line-21" n="21">In Spight of Envy flourish still</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-875-020B-line-22" n="22">And Drapers vie \wt·<hi rend="italics">del</hi>\·with Coopers Hill</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
